@startuml
title TunSociety - Runtime Architecture Overview
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam nodesep 70
skinparam ranksep 70

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor white
  BorderColor #355C7D
  FontColor #102A43
}
skinparam package {
  BackgroundColor #EEF4F8
  BorderColor #486581
  FontColor #243B53
}
skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #355C7D
  FontColor #102A43
}
skinparam cloud {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #355C7D
  FontColor #102A43
}

actor "Guest / Member /\nModerator / Admin" as Client

package "Browser Client" {
  component "Angular Frontend\nGuest pages\nAuth\nUser dashboard\nModerator dashboard\nAdmin dashboard" as Frontend
}

package "ASP.NET Core Backend" {
  component "Controllers\nAuth\nUsers\nPosts\nFriendRequests\nNotifications\nDirectMessages\nModeration\nAdmin" as Controllers
  component "JWT Authentication\n+ Role Policies" as Authz
  component "JwtTokenService" as JwtTokenService
  component "ModerationService" as ModerationService
  component "AiScoringClient" as AiScoringClient
  component "SanctionService" as SanctionService
  component "AuditService" as AuditService
  component "ApplicationDbContext" as ApplicationDbContext
}

database "MySQL\ntunsociety_db" as MySql
cloud "Ollama Local API\nhttp://localhost:11434\nmodel: deepseek-r1" as Ollama
component "Local heuristic\nfallback" as Fallback

Client --> Frontend : uses
Frontend --> Controllers : HTTPS / JSON / JWT

Controllers --> Authz : authorize requests
Controllers --> JwtTokenService : issue login tokens
Controllers --> ModerationService : evaluate submitted text
Controllers --> AuditService : log sensitive actions
Controllers --> ApplicationDbContext : query / save entities

ModerationService --> AiScoringClient : analyze content
ModerationService --> SanctionService : warnings / freezes
AiScoringClient --> Ollama : moderation prompt
AiScoringClient --> Fallback : if local AI fails
ApplicationDbContext --> MySql : persistence

note right of Authz
The backend is the source of truth for roles.
Changing frontend state or browser-inspected values
must not grant Admin or Moderator access.
end note

note bottom of ModerationService
Moderation checks are applied to posts, comments,
direct messages, friend-request notes,
registration full names, and profile display names.
end note
@enduml
